Name: Average time from Accepted + In Progress to Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average time between Accepted + In Progress and Completed + Resolved
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average time until Accepted + In Progress is performed for the first time in a case
Metric: The average of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Average time for Accepted + In Progress grouped by resource
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and the end of case grouped by the last value of org:resource

Name: Average time for Accepted + In Progress grouped by country
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and the end of case grouped by the last value of resource country

Name: Average waiting time to the next activity after Accepted + In Progress

Name: Average time it takes Accepted + In Progress after the execution of Queued + Awaiting Assignment
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Average time it takes the Accepted + In Progress to be done when followed by Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Total time from Accepted + In Progress to Completed + Closed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Total time between Accepted + In Progress and Accepted + Wait - User
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Total time for Accepted + In Progress in variants containing Completed + In Call
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Total time for Accepted + In Progress in variants ending with Completed + Resolved -> Completed + Closed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + Closed occurs

Name: Minimum time between Accepted + In Progress and Completed + In Call
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Minimum time for Accepted + In Progress grouped by organization
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization involved

Name: Minimum time it takes Accepted + In Progress after the execution of Queued + Awaiting Assignment
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Percentage of total case time spent in Accepted + In Progress
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + In Progress and the end of the case

Name: Elapsed time between consecutive Accepted + In Progress activities
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Time until first Accepted + In Progress from case start
Metric: The average of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Time of Accepted + In Progress when preceded by Queued + Awaiting Assignment
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Accepted + In Progress Cycle Time in variants with multiple Accepted + In Progress occurrences
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Average duration of Accepted + In Progress compared to Accepted + Wait - User
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + In Progress and the end of the case

Name: Average duration of Accepted + In Progress compared to Accepted + Assigned
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + In Progress and the end of the case

Name: Average duration of Accepted + In Progress compared to Completed + Resolved
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + In Progress and the end of the case

Name: Ratio of Accepted + In Progress time to total case duration
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + In Progress and the end of the case

Name: Difference between maximum and minimum Accepted + In Progress duration per case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + In Progress and the end of the case

Name: Average time between Accepted + In Progress and subsequent Accepted + Wait - Implementation
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'

Name: Total Accepted + In Progress time in cases with Completed + In Call activity
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Average Accepted + In Progress duration when followed directly by Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Time from first Accepted + In Progress to last Accepted + In Progress in same case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'
